---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="HVAC Services in Red Rock, TX | String Prairie Heating & Air"
	description="Local heating and air conditioning services in Red Rock, Texas. Family-owned HVAC company providing installation, repair, and maintenance in Red Rock and surrounding Bastrop County."
>
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>HVAC Services in Red Rock, TX</h1>
			<p>Your local heating and air conditioning experts</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="area-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="area-intro">
				<h2>Serving Red Rock with Expert HVAC Services</h2>
				<p class="lead">
					Red Rock is a charming rural community in Bastrop County, and String Prairie Heating & Air is proud to serve its residents with professional heating and cooling services. From the farms along FM 20 to the homes near Red Rock Road, we understand the unique HVAC needs of country living and are committed to keeping Red Rock families comfortable year-round.
				</p>
				<p class="lead">
					Whether you need a new system installed, emergency repairs during a Texas heat wave, or regular maintenance to keep your HVAC running efficiently, our experienced technicians are ready to help. We're based nearby in the Rosanky area, which means fast response times for Red Rock customers.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="areas-served">
				<h3>Areas We Serve in Red Rock</h3>
				<p>
					We provide HVAC services throughout the Red Rock community including properties along FM 20, homes near Red Rock Road, ranches and farms in the Red Rock area, properties along Highway 304, and all surrounding rural acreage. Our local presence means we can get to you quickly when you need us most.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="services-overview">
				<h2>Complete HVAC Services for Red Rock Homes & Businesses</h2>
				<div class="services-list">
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Air Conditioning</h3>
						<p>AC installation, repair, maintenance, and emergency service to keep you cool during hot Texas summers.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Heating Systems</h3>
						<p>Furnace and heat pump installation, repair, and maintenance for comfortable winters.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Maintenance Plans</h3>
						<p>Preventive maintenance to extend system life, improve efficiency, and prevent breakdowns.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Emergency Service</h3>
						<p>Fast response when you need it most - we understand HVAC emergencies can't wait.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="local-advantages">
				<h2>Why Red Rock Residents Choose String Prairie</h2>
				<ul class="advantage-list">
					<li>Family-owned and operated - we're part of your community</li>
					<li>Fast local response times for emergencies</li>
					<li>Deep understanding of rural property HVAC needs</li>
					<li>Honest, transparent pricing with no hidden fees</li>
					<li>Fully licensed and insured for your protection</li>
					<li>Expert knowledge of Central Texas climate challenges</li>
					<li>Quality workmanship backed by solid warranties</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="map-section">
				<h2>Find Us on the Map</h2>
				<p class="map-subtitle">Serving Red Rock and all of Bastrop County</p>
				<div class="map-container">
					<iframe
						src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d27593.68!2d-97.45!3d29.95!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x86436f5b3c9e9c9d%3A0x8a8a8a8a8a8a8a8a!2sRed%20Rock%2C%20TX!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1234567890"
						width="100%"
						height="450"
						style="border:0; border-radius: 12px;"
						allowfullscreen=""
						loading="lazy"
						referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
					</iframe>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="testimonials-section">
				<h2>What Red Rock Customers Say</h2>
				<p class="testimonials-subtitle">Hear from your neighbors about their experience with String Prairie Heating & Air</p>
				<div class="testimonials-grid">
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"Living out in Red Rock, we were worried about finding a reliable HVAC company that would actually come out to us. String Prairie exceeded our expectations - fast service and fair prices!"</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Michael T., Red Rock</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"Ron and his team installed a new AC system for us last summer. Professional from start to finish, and the price was very competitive. Highly recommend for anyone in Red Rock!"</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Sarah J., Red Rock</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"Great local company! They've done maintenance on our system twice now and always show up on time and do thorough work. Nice to have a trustworthy HVAC company nearby."</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Kevin & Amy D., Red Rock</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="review-cta">
					<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/String+Prairie+Heating+%26+Air/@29.8918229,-97.3320232" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="review-link">Leave us a Google Review</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section-local">
				<h2>Schedule Your HVAC Service in Red Rock</h2>
				<p>Ready for reliable HVAC service from your local experts? Contact us today!</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="https://book.housecallpro.com/book/String-Prairie-Heating--Air/df82ded280ce43f4a9ee6ee6d36aef76?v2=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Book Online</a>
					<a href="tel:5129249744" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (512) 924-9744</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-blue) 0%, var(--primary-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 5rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.page-header p {
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.area-content {
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}

	.area-intro {
		max-width: 850px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.area-intro h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.areas-served {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, var(--dark-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.areas-served h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.areas-served p {
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		opacity: 0.95;
	}

	.services-overview {
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.services-overview h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.services-list {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.service-item {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-red);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.service-item:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.12);
		border-left-color: var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.service-item h3 {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.service-item p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.local-advantages {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.local-advantages h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.advantage-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		max-width: 750px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.advantage-list li {
		padding: 1rem 0 1rem 2.5rem;
		position: relative;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		font-weight: 300;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.1);
	}

	.advantage-list li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.advantage-list li:before {
		content: "âœ“";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.map-section {
		margin: 4rem 0;
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		background: var(--bg-light);
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	.map-section h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.map-subtitle {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.map-container {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.testimonials-section {
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.testimonials-section h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.testimonials-subtitle {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.testimonials-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.testimonial-card {
		background: white;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
		border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-red);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.testimonial-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.12);
		border-left-color: var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.stars {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		color: #f59e0b;
	}

	.testimonial-text {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.testimonial-author {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.review-cta {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.review-link {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, var(--dark-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 50px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.3);
	}

	.review-link:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.4);
	}

	.cta-section-local {
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-red) 0%, var(--dark-red) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	.cta-section-local h2 {
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.cta-section-local p {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.btn {
		padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		display: inline-block;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: white;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: transparent;
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid white;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background: white;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		transform: translateY(-3px);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-header h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.area-intro h2,
		.services-overview h2,
		.local-advantages h2,
		.map-section h2,
		.testimonials-section h2,
		.cta-section-local h2 {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}

		.services-list {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.map-section {
			padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.testimonials-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
